Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:25.98,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Adapted from novel of the same name, "The Grave Robbers' Chronicles (Dao Mu Bi Ji): Bronze Tree of Death" by Nanpai Sanshu\NOriginal work by Nanpai Sanshu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.54,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Chief Producer: Cheng Wu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:32.78,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Producer: Zou Zhengyu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:43.98,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,936)}The Grave Robbers' Chronicles  (Dao Mu Bi Ji): Bronze Tree of Death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:45.82,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,An endless road ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:50.26,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Two extremities of love and loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:54.98,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Inner demons shrouding the heart—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.38,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,they wallow in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:02.18,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where is my old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:06.26,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,He is lingering in the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:13.10,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,convinced that he hasn't veered too far off course, in this world of fleeting destinies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:19.74,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you pine? Why do you yearn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:24.30,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Nowhere to turn—it's a path of no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:28.54,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,The way of life is vicious, we keep going in circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:30.86,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Hard to discern the truths from the lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.94,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,tell the evil from the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:36.42,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,In front of my eyes, a gnarled mess of mountains and waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:41.10,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why do you tread a path this treacherous?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:45.34,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,Embroiled in sinister schemes, in trepidation as the tables turn and turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.82,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,I bid you adieu—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:51.54,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,shall we never meet again!
