Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:13.43,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Time has
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:17.52,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,drowned out even the claps of thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:19.35,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,They scatter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:23.31,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the cut-up fragments of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:29.14,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I can only fumble around, trying to piece them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:33.14,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Why must I climb mountains and peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.97,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,to collect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.97,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,the shadows of hanging onto someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.02,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,however late I always seem to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:47.81,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Those places where I once walked,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:52.02,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,what did they
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.97,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,look like originally?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:24:03.64,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Trying to trace those footsteps behind me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:07.81,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,I have forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:13.14,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,as the path I came from was too far and too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:19.14,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will be the end of my journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:23.22,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:27.14,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.93,0:24:30.27,ED_EN1,,0,0,0,,Where will it be...
